posting_body: ['We are doing in-person and virtual tours.', 'We offer 2 bedroom 1 bath apartments at Fountain Terrace Apartments.', 'Our residents are responsible for electricity only!', 'FREE WIFI IN EVERY BUILDING!!!', 'Units available for move now upon approval!', 'I currently have a 2nd floor unit with a western facing balcony to sit out and enjoy the sunset.', 'This unit has been recently renovated with espresso brown cabinets, stainless steel appliances including an above range microwave and dishwasher.', 'Rent is $1375 a month!', 'Fountain Terrace is highly rated in New Brighton for being one of the most affordable options in the area!!', 'Garages and extra storage space', 'available for an additional monthly charge', '24 HR Emergency Maintenance', '** availability changes daily please speak with the onsite manager for current details', 'Smoke-free Property', '*2 pets per unit limit, additional deposit, and monthly animal rent', 'Fountain Terrace is highly rated in New Brighton for being one of the most affordable options in the area!!', 'Amenities:', 'Rent includes heat, water, sewer, trash, and recycling', 'Laundry facilities on every floor']
